thread.title: Huon & Cath
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Huon & Cath

author: Huon & Cath
title: Huon & Cath
text:
James Pilliner from the Carlton office was fantastic to deal with. He kept us informed throughout the whole process, and was open and honest.
He did a terrific job as auctioneer too. A credit to Nelson Alexander and someone we would use again and again, and will highly recommend to anyone selling a house!
